description:
This is the debut PFP series of the Whyland ecosystem, marking the first collaboration between Whyland and a Web-2 brand - and it's is only the beginning of what is to come! 

Prepare for an extraordinary journey in the Whyland universe as 7 captivating characters, each with their own intriguing backstory, are ready to embark on thrilling adventures. Get ready to join forces with them, gear up, and dive into a world filled with wonder and excitement! Let's set off together on this exhilarating quest like no other!
name: KUKA by WHYLAND
